{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1033,"text":"\"Can you taste words?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":3980,"text":"It was a question\nthat caught me by surprise."},{"time":7060,"text":"This summer, I was giving a talk\nat a literary festival,"},{"time":10195,"text":"and afterwards, as I was signing books,"},{"time":12895,"text":"a teenage girl came with her friend,"},{"time":15598,"text":"and this is what she asked me."},{"time":17655,"text":"I told her that some people\nexperience an overlap in their senses"},{"time":22496,"text":"so that they could hear colors"},{"time":24347,"text":"or see sounds,"},{"time":25899,"text":"and many writers were fascinated\nby this subject, myself included."},{"time":31361,"text":"But she cut me off, a bit impatiently,\nand said, \"Yeah, I know all of that."},{"time":36254,"text":"It's called synesthesia.\nWe learned it at school."},{"time":39566,"text":"But my mom is reading your book,"},{"time":42019,"text":"and she says there's lots\nof food and ingredients"},{"time":45494,"text":"and a long dinner scene in it."},{"time":47402,"text":"She gets hungry at every page."},{"time":49592,"text":"So I was thinking,"},{"time":51162,"text":"how come you don't\nget hungry when you write?"},{"time":53418,"text":"And I thought maybe,\nmaybe you could taste words."},{"time":57010,"text":"Does it make sense?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":58881,"text":"And, actually, it did make sense,"},{"time":61080,"text":"because ever since my childhood,"},{"time":63211,"text":"each letter in the alphabet\nhas a different color,"},{"time":66908,"text":"and colors bring me flavors."},{"time":69461,"text":"So for instance, the color purple\nis quite pungent, almost perfumed,"},{"time":75091,"text":"and any words that I associate with purple"},{"time":78932,"text":"taste the same way,"},{"time":81122,"text":"such as \"sunset\" -- a very spicy word."},{"time":85451,"text":"But I was worried that if I tell\nall of this to the teenager,"},{"time":90173,"text":"it might sound either too abstract"},{"time":92347,"text":"or perhaps too weird,"},{"time":95135,"text":"and there wasn't enough time anyhow,"},{"time":96899,"text":"because people were waiting in the queue,"},{"time":99184,"text":"so it suddenly felt like\nwhat I was trying to convey"},{"time":103740,"text":"was more complicated and detailed"},{"time":106813,"text":"than what the circumstances\nallowed me to say."},{"time":111572,"text":"And I did what I usually do\nin similar situations:"},{"time":115823,"text":"I stammered, I shut down,\nand I stopped talking."},{"time":119452,"text":"I stopped talking because\nthe truth was complicated,"},{"time":123642,"text":"even though I knew, deep within,"},{"time":126093,"text":"that one should never, ever\nremain silent for fear of complexity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132522,"text":"So I want to start my talk today"},{"time":134407,"text":"with the answer that I was not able\nto give on that day."},{"time":137952,"text":"Yes, I can taste words --"},{"time":140273,"text":"sometimes, that is, not always,"},{"time":142437,"text":"and happy words have\na different flavor than sad words."},{"time":146485,"text":"I like to explore: What does\nthe word \"creativity\" taste like,"},{"time":151176,"text":"or \"equality,\""},{"time":153214,"text":"\"love,\" \"revolution?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":155684,"text":"And what about \"motherland?\""},{"time":158358,"text":"These days, it's particularly\nthis last word that troubles me."},{"time":162626,"text":"It leaves a sweet taste on my tongue,"},{"time":165219,"text":"like cinnamon, a bit of rose water"},{"time":168629,"text":"and golden apples."},{"time":170053,"text":"But underneath, there's a sharp tang,"},{"time":173275,"text":"like nettles and dandelion."},{"time":175899,"text":"The taste of my motherland, Turkey,"},{"time":179210,"text":"is a mixture of sweet and bitter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183730,"text":"And the reason why I'm telling you this"},{"time":185696,"text":"is because I think\nthere's more and more people"},{"time":188143,"text":"all around the world today"},{"time":189959,"text":"who have similarly mixed emotions"},{"time":192848,"text":"about the lands they come from."},{"time":195144,"text":"We love our native countries, yeah?"},{"time":197829,"text":"How can we not?"},{"time":199053,"text":"We feel attached to the people,\nthe culture, the land, the food."},{"time":203518,"text":"And yet at the same time,"},{"time":204734,"text":"we feel increasingly frustrated\nby its politics and politicians,"},{"time":210440,"text":"sometimes to the point\nof despair or hurt or anger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216088,"text":"I want to talk about emotions"},{"time":218240,"text":"and the need to boost\nour emotional intelligence."},{"time":221997,"text":"I think it's a pity"},{"time":223172,"text":"that mainstream political theory\npays very little attention to emotions."},{"time":229199,"text":"Oftentimes, analysts and experts\nare so busy with data and metrics"},{"time":234817,"text":"that they seem to forget\nthose things in life"},{"time":237778,"text":"that are difficult to measure"},{"time":239636,"text":"and perhaps impossible to cluster\nunder statistical models."},{"time":244925,"text":"But I think this is a mistake,\nfor two main reasons."},{"time":248314,"text":"Firstly, because we are emotional beings."},{"time":251180,"text":"As human beings,\nI think we all are like that."},{"time":254727,"text":"But secondly, and this is new,"},{"time":257425,"text":"we have entered\na new stage in world history"},{"time":261104,"text":"in which collective sentiments\nguide and misguide politics"},{"time":267147,"text":"more than ever before."},{"time":269951,"text":"And through social media\nand social networking,"},{"time":273095,"text":"these sentiments are further amplified,"},{"time":276005,"text":"polarized, and they travel\naround the world quite fast."},{"time":280315,"text":"Ours is the age of anxiety, anger,"},{"time":284254,"text":"distrust, resentment"},{"time":286792,"text":"and, I think, lots of fear."},{"time":289112,"text":"But here's the thing:"},{"time":290431,"text":"even though there's plenty of research\nabout economic factors,"},{"time":295230,"text":"there's relatively few studies\nabout emotional factors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300195,"text":"Why is it that we underestimate\nfeelings and perceptions?"},{"time":305363,"text":"I think it's going to be one\nof our biggest intellectual challenges,"},{"time":309377,"text":"because our political systems\nare replete with emotions."},{"time":314701,"text":"In country after country,"},{"time":316531,"text":"we have seen illiberal politicians\nexploiting these emotions."},{"time":321967,"text":"And yet within the academia\nand among the intelligentsia,"},{"time":325609,"text":"we are yet to take emotions seriously."},{"time":329199,"text":"I think we should."},{"time":330497,"text":"And just like we should focus\non economic inequality worldwide,"},{"time":334386,"text":"we need to pay more attention\nto emotional and cognitive gaps worldwide"},{"time":341026,"text":"and how to bridge these gaps,"},{"time":342860,"text":"because they do matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345734,"text":"Years ago, when I was still\nliving in Istanbul,"},{"time":348508,"text":"an American scholar working on\nwomen writers in the Middle East"},{"time":352568,"text":"came to see me."},{"time":354504,"text":"And at some point\nin our exchange, she said,"},{"time":357053,"text":"\"I understand why you're a feminist,"},{"time":359033,"text":"because, you know, you live in Turkey.\""},{"time":362529,"text":"And I said to her,"},{"time":363711,"text":"\"I don't understand\nwhy you're not a feminist,"},{"time":365983,"text":"because, you know, you live in America.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":368259,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":370803,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":373789,"text":"And she laughed."},{"time":376290,"text":"She took it as a joke,"},{"time":377898,"text":"and the moment passed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379741,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":381662,"text":"But the way she had divided the world\ninto two imaginary camps,"},{"time":386596,"text":"into two opposite camps --"},{"time":388563,"text":"it bothered me and it stayed with me."},{"time":391227,"text":"According to this imaginary map,"},{"time":393747,"text":"some parts of the world\nwere liquid countries."},{"time":397293,"text":"They were like choppy waters\nnot yet settled."},{"time":400587,"text":"Some other parts of the world,\nnamely the West,"},{"time":403922,"text":"were solid, safe and stable."},{"time":407251,"text":"So it was the liquid lands\nthat needed feminism"},{"time":410589,"text":"and activism and human rights,"},{"time":413010,"text":"and those of us who were\nunfortunate enough"},{"time":415432,"text":"to come from such places"},{"time":417268,"text":"had to keep struggling\nfor these most essential values."},{"time":422066,"text":"But there was hope."},{"time":423277,"text":"Since history moved forward,"},{"time":425108,"text":"even the most unsteady lands\nwould someday catch up."},{"time":429521,"text":"And meanwhile, the citizens of solid lands"},{"time":432543,"text":"could take comfort\nin the progress of history"},{"time":436739,"text":"and in the triumph of the liberal order."},{"time":440013,"text":"They could support the struggles\nof other people elsewhere,"},{"time":444000,"text":"but they themselves\ndid not have to struggle"},{"time":447550,"text":"for the basics of democracy anymore,"},{"time":450902,"text":"because they were beyond that stage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454704,"text":"I think in the year 2016,"},{"time":457173,"text":"this hierarchical geography\nwas shattered to pieces."},{"time":462324,"text":"Our world no longer follows\nthis dualistic pattern"},{"time":466438,"text":"in the scholar's mind, if it ever did."},{"time":470056,"text":"Now we know that history\ndoes not necessarily move forward."},{"time":474439,"text":"Sometimes it draws circles,"},{"time":476386,"text":"even slides backwards,"},{"time":478367,"text":"and that generations\ncan make the same mistakes"},{"time":481338,"text":"that their great-grandfathers had made."},{"time":484196,"text":"And now we know that there's no such thing"},{"time":486827,"text":"as solid countries\nversus liquid countries."},{"time":490658,"text":"In fact, we are all living\nin liquid times,"},{"time":495126,"text":"just like the late Zygmunt Bauman told us."},{"time":498797,"text":"And Bauman had another\ndefinition for our age."},{"time":502013,"text":"He used to say we are all going\nto be walking on moving sands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508232,"text":"And if that's the case, I think,"},{"time":510490,"text":"it should concern us women more than men,"},{"time":513815,"text":"because when societies\nslide backwards into authoritarianism,"},{"time":517929,"text":"nationalism or religious fanaticism,"},{"time":520749,"text":"women have much more to lose."},{"time":523640,"text":"That is why this needs\nto be a vital moment,"},{"time":526485,"text":"not only for global activism,"},{"time":528700,"text":"but in my opinion,\nfor global sisterhood as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532583,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540735,"text":"But I want to make a little confession\nbefore I go any further."},{"time":544107,"text":"Until recently, whenever I took part in\nan international conference or festival,"},{"time":549312,"text":"I would be usually one\nof the more depressed speakers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553527,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":554809,"text":"Having seen how our dreams of democracy\nand how our dreams of coexistence"},{"time":560657,"text":"were crushed in Turkey,"},{"time":562644,"text":"both gradually but also\nwith a bewildering speed,"},{"time":566897,"text":"over the years I've felt\nquite demoralized."},{"time":569911,"text":"And at these festivals there would be\nsome other gloomy writers,"},{"time":574048,"text":"and they would come from places\nsuch as Egypt, Nigeria, Pakistan,"},{"time":578991,"text":"Bangladesh, Philippines,\nChina, Venezuela, Russia."},{"time":584036,"text":"And we would smile\nat each other in sympathy,"},{"time":586413,"text":"this camaraderie of the doomed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588534,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":591165,"text":"And you could call us WADWIC:"},{"time":593393,"text":"Worried and Depressed\nWriters International Club."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597535,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":599281,"text":"But then things began to change,"},{"time":601076,"text":"and suddenly our club became more popular,"},{"time":605063,"text":"and we started to have new members."},{"time":607596,"text":"I remember --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":609069,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":611555,"text":"I remember Greek writers and poets\njoined first, came on board."},{"time":616825,"text":"And then writers from Hungary and Poland,"},{"time":620606,"text":"and then, interestingly, writers\nfrom Austria, the Netherlands, France,"},{"time":626102,"text":"and then writers from the UK,\nwhere I live and where I call my home,"},{"time":630561,"text":"and then writers from the USA."},{"time":634667,"text":"Suddenly, there were more of us"},{"time":636734,"text":"feeling worried about\nthe fate of our nations"},{"time":639541,"text":"and the future of the world."},{"time":641827,"text":"And maybe there were more of us now"},{"time":644357,"text":"feeling like strangers\nin our own motherlands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648624,"text":"And then this bizarre thing happened."},{"time":650825,"text":"Those of us who used to be\nvery depressed for a long time,"},{"time":654336,"text":"we started to feel less depressed,"},{"time":657082,"text":"whereas the newcomers,\nthey were so not used to feeling this way"},{"time":660808,"text":"that they were now even more depressed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662884,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":664003,"text":"So you could see writers\nfrom Bangladesh or Turkey or Egypt"},{"time":668865,"text":"trying to console their colleagues"},{"time":672319,"text":"from Brexit Britain\nor from post-election USA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":676802,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":679230,"text":"But joking aside,"},{"time":680501,"text":"I think our world is full\nof unprecedented challenges,"},{"time":684922,"text":"and this comes with an emotional backlash,"},{"time":687984,"text":"because in the face of high-speed change,"},{"time":690229,"text":"many people wish to slow down,"},{"time":692320,"text":"and when there's too much unfamiliarity,"},{"time":694912,"text":"people long for the familiar."},{"time":697373,"text":"And when things get too confusing,"},{"time":699643,"text":"many people crave simplicity."},{"time":702707,"text":"This is a very dangerous crossroads,"},{"time":705168,"text":"because it's exactly where the demagogue\nenters into the picture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711447,"text":"The demagogue understands\nhow collective sentiments work"},{"time":715338,"text":"and how he -- it's usually a he --\ncan benefit from them."},{"time":719999,"text":"He tells us that we all\nbelong in our tribes,"},{"time":723613,"text":"and he tells us that we will be safer\nif we are surrounded by sameness."},{"time":729345,"text":"Demagogues come in all sizes\nand in all shapes."},{"time":732129,"text":"This could be the eccentric leader\nof a marginal political party"},{"time":736464,"text":"somewhere in Europe,"},{"time":737824,"text":"or an Islamist extremist imam\npreaching dogma and hatred,"},{"time":743570,"text":"or it could be a white supremacist\nNazi-admiring orator somewhere else."},{"time":749294,"text":"All these figures, at first glance --\nthey seem disconnected."},{"time":753470,"text":"But I think they feed each other,"},{"time":755894,"text":"and they need each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758687,"text":"And all around the world,"},{"time":759927,"text":"when we look at how demagogues talk\nand how they inspire movements,"},{"time":765716,"text":"I think they have one\nunmistakable quality in common:"},{"time":770070,"text":"they strongly, strongly dislike plurality."},{"time":774580,"text":"They cannot deal with multiplicity."},{"time":777848,"text":"Adorno used to say,"},{"time":779470,"text":"\"Intolerance of ambiguity is the sign\nof an authoritarian personality.\""},{"time":786709,"text":"But I ask myself:"},{"time":788071,"text":"What if that same sign,"},{"time":790058,"text":"that same intolerance of ambiguity --"},{"time":793235,"text":"what if it's the mark of our times,\nof the age we're living in?"},{"time":798631,"text":"Because wherever I look,\nI see nuances withering away."},{"time":802519,"text":"On TV shows, we have\none anti-something speaker"},{"time":806577,"text":"situated against a pro-something speaker."},{"time":809821,"text":"Yeah? It's good ratings."},{"time":811329,"text":"It's even better\nif they shout at each other."},{"time":814101,"text":"Even in academia, where our intellect\nis supposed to be nourished,"},{"time":818676,"text":"you see one atheist scholar\ncompeting with a firmly theist scholar,"},{"time":824975,"text":"but it's not a real intellectual exchange,"},{"time":827963,"text":"because it's a clash\nbetween two certainties."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832183,"text":"I think binary oppositions are everywhere."},{"time":836719,"text":"So slowly and systematically,"},{"time":839264,"text":"we are being denied the right\nto be complex."},{"time":844485,"text":"Istanbul, Berlin, Nice, Paris, Brussels,"},{"time":848112,"text":"Dhaka, Baghdad, Barcelona:"},{"time":850782,"text":"we have seen one horrible\nterror attack after another."},{"time":854685,"text":"And when you express your sorrow,\nand when you react against the cruelty,"},{"time":859101,"text":"you get all kinds of reactions,"},{"time":860967,"text":"messages on social media."},{"time":863046,"text":"But one of them is quite disturbing,"},{"time":864906,"text":"only because it's so widespread."},{"time":867128,"text":"They say, \"Why do you feel sorry for them?"},{"time":871572,"text":"Why do you feel sorry for them?"},{"time":873776,"text":"Why don't you feel sorry\nfor civilians in Yemen"},{"time":876742,"text":"or civilians in Syria?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":879973,"text":"And I think the people\nwho write such messages"},{"time":882397,"text":"do not understand"},{"time":883877,"text":"that we can feel sorry for\nand stand in solidarity with"},{"time":888948,"text":"victims of terrorism and violence\nin the Middle East, in Europe,"},{"time":893593,"text":"in Asia, in America, wherever, everywhere,"},{"time":896553,"text":"equally and simultaneously."},{"time":899184,"text":"They don't seem to understand\nthat we don't have to pick one pain"},{"time":902942,"text":"and one place over all others."},{"time":907040,"text":"But I think this is what\ntribalism does to us."},{"time":910647,"text":"It shrinks our minds, for sure,"},{"time":912980,"text":"but it also shrinks our hearts,"},{"time":915126,"text":"to such an extent that we become numb\nto the suffering of other people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":921700,"text":"And the sad truth is,\nwe weren't always like this."},{"time":924688,"text":"I had a children's book out in Turkey,"},{"time":928724,"text":"and when the book was published,\nI did lots of events."},{"time":931723,"text":"I went to many primary schools,"},{"time":933357,"text":"which gave me a chance to observe\nyounger kids in Turkey."},{"time":937273,"text":"And it was always amazing to see\nhow much empathy, imagination"},{"time":942139,"text":"and chutzpah they have."},{"time":943603,"text":"These children are much more inclined\nto become global citizens"},{"time":947654,"text":"than nationalists at that age."},{"time":950184,"text":"And it's wonderful to see,\nwhen you ask them,"},{"time":952305,"text":"so many of them want\nto be poets and writers,"},{"time":955420,"text":"and girls are just as confident as boys,"},{"time":958842,"text":"if not even more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":960806,"text":"But then I would go to high schools,"},{"time":963009,"text":"and everything has changed."},{"time":964848,"text":"Now nobody wants to be a writer anymore,"},{"time":967038,"text":"now nobody wants to be a novelist anymore,"},{"time":969498,"text":"and girls have become timid,"},{"time":972276,"text":"they are cautious, guarded,"},{"time":974434,"text":"reluctant to speak up in the public space,"},{"time":977698,"text":"because we have taught them --"},{"time":979398,"text":"the family, the school, the society --"},{"time":981871,"text":"we have taught them\nto erase their individuality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":986046,"text":"I think East and West,"},{"time":987391,"text":"we are losing multiplicity,"},{"time":989971,"text":"both within our societies\nand within ourselves."},{"time":994532,"text":"And coming from Turkey,\nI do know that the loss of diversity"},{"time":998767,"text":"is a major, major loss."},{"time":1001278,"text":"Today, my motherland became\nthe world's biggest jailer"},{"time":1004629,"text":"for journalists,"},{"time":1005993,"text":"surpassing even China's sad record."},{"time":1010290,"text":"And I also believe that what happened\nover there in Turkey"},{"time":1015708,"text":"can happen anywhere."},{"time":1017185,"text":"It can even happen here."},{"time":1019647,"text":"So just like solid countries\nwas an illusion,"},{"time":1023897,"text":"singular identities is also an illusion,"},{"time":1028232,"text":"because we all have\na multiplicity of voices inside."},{"time":1034045,"text":"The Iranian, the Persian poet, Hafiz,"},{"time":1037410,"text":"used to say, \"You carry in your soul\nevery ingredient necessary"},{"time":1042818,"text":"to turn your existence into joy."},{"time":1045723,"text":"All you have to do\nis to mix those ingredients.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1049489,"text":"And I think mix we can."},{"time":1051490,"text":"I am an Istanbulite,"},{"time":1054626,"text":"but I'm also attached to the Balkans,"},{"time":1056813,"text":"the Aegean, the Mediterranean,"},{"time":1059237,"text":"the Middle East, the Levant."},{"time":1061561,"text":"I am a European by birth, by choice,"},{"time":1064356,"text":"the values that I uphold."},{"time":1066620,"text":"I have become a Londoner over the years."},{"time":1069217,"text":"I would like to think of myself\nas a global soul, as a world citizen,"},{"time":1073981,"text":"a nomad and an itinerant storyteller."},{"time":1078000,"text":"I have multiple attachments,\njust like all of us do."},{"time":1081781,"text":"And multiple attachments\nmean multiple stories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1086628,"text":"As writers, we always\nchase stories, of course,"},{"time":1091361,"text":"but I think we are also\ninterested in silences,"},{"time":1094479,"text":"the things we cannot talk about,"},{"time":1096562,"text":"political taboos, cultural taboos."},{"time":1099559,"text":"We're also interested in our own silences."},{"time":1103560,"text":"I have always been very vocal\nabout and written extensively"},{"time":1107675,"text":"about minority rights, women's rights,"},{"time":1110744,"text":"LGBT rights."},{"time":1112800,"text":"But as I was thinking about this TED Talk,"},{"time":1115893,"text":"I realized one thing:"},{"time":1117480,"text":"I have never had the courage\nto say in a public space"},{"time":1122414,"text":"that I was bisexual myself,"},{"time":1125641,"text":"because I so feared the slander"},{"time":1128792,"text":"and the stigma and the ridicule"},{"time":1131324,"text":"and the hatred that was sure to follow."},{"time":1134800,"text":"But of course, one should never,\never, remain silent"},{"time":1139366,"text":"for fear of complexity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1142662,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1150503,"text":"And although I am\nno stranger to anxieties,"},{"time":1153830,"text":"and although I am talking here\nabout the power of emotions --"},{"time":1157600,"text":"I do know the power of emotions --"},{"time":1159676,"text":"I have discovered over time"},{"time":1161627,"text":"that emotions are not limitless."},{"time":1163801,"text":"You know? They have a limit."},{"time":1165579,"text":"There comes a moment --"},{"time":1166878,"text":"it's like a tipping point\nor a threshold --"},{"time":1169025,"text":"when you get tired of feeling afraid,"},{"time":1172172,"text":"when you get tired of feeling anxious."},{"time":1174868,"text":"And I think not only individuals,"},{"time":1176787,"text":"but perhaps nations, too,\nhave their own tipping points."},{"time":1181865,"text":"So even stronger than my emotions"},{"time":1184617,"text":"is my awareness"},{"time":1186542,"text":"that not only gender, not only identity,"},{"time":1190215,"text":"but life itself is fluid."},{"time":1193651,"text":"They want to divide us into tribes,"},{"time":1196389,"text":"but we are connected across borders."},{"time":1199391,"text":"They preach certainty,"},{"time":1201093,"text":"but we know that life has plenty of magic"},{"time":1204718,"text":"and plenty of ambiguity."},{"time":1206788,"text":"And they like to incite dualities,"},{"time":1209603,"text":"but we are far more nuanced than that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1213560,"text":"So what can we do?"},{"time":1215103,"text":"I think we need to go back to the basics,"},{"time":1217445,"text":"back to the colors of the alphabet."},{"time":1220217,"text":"The Lebanese poet\nKhalil Gibran used to say,"},{"time":1224001,"text":"\"I learned silence from the talkative"},{"time":1226818,"text":"and tolerance from the intolerant"},{"time":1229282,"text":"and kindness from the unkind.\""},{"time":1232152,"text":"I think it's a great motto for our times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1235274,"text":"So from populist demagogues, we will learn"},{"time":1238759,"text":"the indispensability of democracy."},{"time":1241499,"text":"And from isolationists, we will learn\nthe need for global solidarity."},{"time":1246257,"text":"And from tribalists, we will learn\nthe beauty of cosmopolitanism"},{"time":1251762,"text":"and the beauty of diversity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1255403,"text":"As I finish, I want to leave you\nwith one word, or one taste."},{"time":1260661,"text":"The word \"yurt\" in Turkish\nmeans \"motherland.\""},{"time":1264370,"text":"It means \"homeland.\""},{"time":1266065,"text":"But interestingly, the word also means"},{"time":1268368,"text":"\"a tent used by nomadic tribes.\""},{"time":1272146,"text":"And I like that combination,\nbecause it makes me think"},{"time":1275228,"text":"homelands do not need\nto be rooted in one place."},{"time":1279328,"text":"They can be portable."},{"time":1280816,"text":"We can take them with us everywhere."},{"time":1283549,"text":"And I think for writers, for storytellers,"},{"time":1286496,"text":"at the end of the day,"},{"time":1287932,"text":"there is one main homeland,"},{"time":1290381,"text":"and it's called \"Storyland.\""},{"time":1293143,"text":"And the taste of that word"},{"time":1295467,"text":"is the taste of freedom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1297795,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1299122,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}